{
  "stem": "19218.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The town was approximately-- before the war, before 1939, we had approximately 25,000 population spread out, quite a bit spread out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was small, but-- but the Jewish population at that time, we had about 120 families.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had one synagogue.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course I never knew that there was any other synagogue besides an Orthodox synagogue, so of course I was brought up in an Orthodox way.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I probably attended Hebrew school [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from the time I probably could start walking, maybe at three years of age.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my secular education stopped when I was 11.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I never attended a strictly Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I went to public school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But after school, of course, I used to go to Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So all of my religious education stopped at 11 years of age.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So whatever I have acquired was until 11 years of age, because at that time I stopped simply because the public school was more demanding, and I was very active in extracurricular activity, in school, too, singing in a choir, sports activities.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So of course, I-- I-- I didn't have the time or-- or really the desire to go and continue with the Jewish education.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somehow, though, I have retained must-- most of my secular education.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And although I've never had another Hebrew lesson since I was 11 years of age, I-- I know my Bible quite well.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know my Hebrew reading and my prayers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I retained it all with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm even surprised myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I guess when you learn when you're young, your mind absorbs anything and everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's like a sponge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I probably was a good student, so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Excuse me for one second.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[DRINKS] My father's name was [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was called Hersh Leib.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
